today has been ...weird?... i got droped off at jeffs around 12. and after a few hours for omse reason my emotions just went nuts..like i started feelign like i was gonna cry and i felt bad and i had no idea why... so me and jeff went inside and her understood i didnt want to do much of anyhting so we laid on the couch on started watching a movie...and he started kissing me and whispered " promise me you'll stay with me forever"...i was like AWWWWW!!!!!!!!! " of course i will" lol....i thought that was just the sweetest thing..then an hour later my friend cameron comes over and hangs out for a lil bit...and i went home not to long after.im not goin back to jeffs untill friday:( .. and i start cross country on monday at 8:30 in the morning...god thats gonna suck..the coach was tellin me to try and get more girls into it lol..

ok so my aunt lori is goin to visit everyone in south carolina thursday morning at 4 in the morning so i have a ride back!! YAY!! i cant stand it down here!!  and i miss jeff terribly..just like 20 minutes ago my sister called to talk to my mom and i answered and she was a littel suprised and she only called to tell my mom she was gonna be gone for a few days and then she started telling me about some stupid shit buddy did witch it tottaly fucked up! and i know my sister will always love that boy to death and iv had my sister cry to me b-4 but not like she did tonight..i almost started crying because it was so sad..my sister and my dad never really got along and she's even telling me how she miss's him alot witch came to total shock for me. she wants to be daddys littel girl again. witch i can understand because my dad does love his kids with everyhting he has. i know everyone who knows our family would disagree with me but u have to know my dad like i do. my dad will talk to me about us sometimes and it opens my eyes, he's even cried over us b-4.. he cried when i left one summer from visiting him and thats when it really hit me. i use to be a bitch and always say i hate my dad and he's to strict and all this crap. but when i look around at the kids i use to hangout with and wanted their parents to be mine so bad im glad they wernt.. their lives have gone to hell, their all tied up in drugs and screwin just about anyone they can and stuff. and me on the other hand who had the "strict" dad, is doing the best iv ever been. i can honestly say without my dad i would be one of those kids who i thought had cool parents when i use to live down here. My dad is the only reason i love my life right now. He's the one who buys me uniforms and stuff so i can play soccer and he's the one who let me go out with the guy i love "although my dad would call it puppy love, lol" He gives me $20 just for doing dishes and cleaning up the bathroom witch i know should only be like a $10 allowence but that fact is its not. and he actually cares about how im doing in school so i dont slip and start failing everyhting, he helps me stay on top. He actually listens now, i mean im sure he always did before but i only wanted to hear what i wanted i didnt want to listen to him because it wasnt what i wanted. now i see his reasoning on most things. and me and my step mom get along real good. i talk to her about almost everything now i didnt notice that shes been through alot of the same stuff too. shes a good listener. and i love my littel brother with all my heart. when im up there he anouys me and i hate it but my mom made a good point and made me think back when i always wanted to be with the older kids with my sisters and stuff and they would make me leave and id be really sad. i dont think i know anyone who dosnt like herbie. he really is a good kid, he has a temper sometimes but he seems to be getting better at it.
wow i think this it the longest entry iv ever wrote..i dont expect anyone to read this i just had to write that all down.

i hate when my dad says " oh i you clean this and that then ill give you allowence for the weekends" and the first thin i think is hell yea i get monye on friday...you know. the day that MOST teenagers freakin go out with friends and shit. but ooohhh nooooo i have to wait untill saturday when he said i couldnt go anywhere. what the hell man. i doubt he's gonna give me money at all.today me and jeffrey got in a argument. my fault mostly. his x came up to me and started bitchin at me and then we started talkin minus the shouting, and i got pretty upset because i thought jeffrey was lieing to me about some stuff. so i couldnt stand to be around her anymore so i walked otu of our gym and sat on the middle school steps then went to his bus 5 minutes b-4 school let out and i went off. i said " DID YOU LIE TO ME!!??" him " what are you talking about?" me "SAMANTHA SAID U DID!" him " well she lied cas i didnt." me " DONT FUCKING LIE TO ME, ATLEAST TELL ME THE FUCKING TRUTH!!" thats when my friend walked up and we continued arguing, then he started walking off and i snatched his arm and he just looked at me all mad and shit so i let go and gave him a hug and started walking to my bus. then he called later and he started crying because i was still being a bitch because im a fucking retard. i cried the whole bus ride home. and the slipknot song i was listenign to didnt help any. it was sad and it made me calm though.i was sitting down on this wood thing outside my house and i was thinkign how stupid i was acting to him at school and it pissed me off so i started hitting the wodd and have 3 bruised knuckles and 1 cut one. i havnt told jeffrey though, i dont plan to either. i dont want him worrying about it.

Yesturday was me and jeff's 3 month aniv. it started out ok and all and then he started feelig sick or so he said.Then it got good then he started getting pissed because his sister's boyfriend type thing pissed him off. so we went to his house and it was all good and we were happy then we had to go to the park across the street from his house because his mom was leaving and she didnt trust us lol.so we sat there and talked. one thing he told me that really shocked me was he said " sometimes i just lay and think about what if u left me, and i cry" i almost cried for him saying that lol...i never in a life time thought he would have told me something like that..He also told me he wanted to be withme untill the day i die..i was confused because he said untill the day i die instead of the day he dies. oh well.He also said he wants to marry me and purpose to me and stuff btu he knows ill say no right now. and he's right i would say no right now. i want for him to wait atleast a year and then make his decision on that.realationships are always awsome for the first 3 months, if they are still the same in a year that they were in the first 3 months then hell yea its a good match.Well im gonna go watch a movie and just chill because im sick and abotut o loose my voice lol

But i got to see jeff after school. i made him go to some stupid soccer party thing with me lol..i beat his ass at soccer today so many times lol, but i will give him props for beating me 2 times. after the soccer party we went to this one prep party we got invited to because jeff had to make sure frank was still stayin the night then we ditched that place real qwik lol... went to our friend genes house and chilled there for a lil while. then got a ride back to the party so i was able to get picked up. and while we were waiting all the littel skate boarders were out there was 9 of them lol. and of course jeff started skateing. then jeff jumped into a water fountain and gave me a hug after i ran form him because he was soaking wet. then he decided it would be funny to skateboard in his boxer lol so he did it lol.. i swear he is our entertainment lol...he's great.
